⁠
If you don’t know Connie Diiamond, allow us to put you on.⁠ The Bronx rapper is ready to take over the charts with witty lyricism over drill beats and a range of cadences that go from relentlessly aggressive to endearingly flirty. With cosigns from Fivio Foreign, Fabolos, Remy Ma, and more, Connie Diiamond is one to pay attention to. Make sure to check out her latest EP, “Gift Raps”, out now.⁠
⁠
